The paper focuses on improving the classification of security bug reports using machine learning techniques, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and computer security (cs.CR) categories. The paper also mentions the use of text analytics and hyperparameter optimization, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses data pre-processing methods, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
